snippet.title: “AMBER’S DONE” Amber Heard's Top 10 Reasons SHE GOT CANCELLED | The Gossipy
snippet.description:
Amber Heard's Top 10 Reasons SHE GOT CANCELLED | The Gossipy

Amber Heard and Johnny Depp have been at the forefront of celebrity news these past few years. Their stories of their Amber Heard Johnny Depp's toxic relationship and harrowing divorce being the center of celeb news. For a while Amber Heard had people believing her as the victim of the situation, but as more and more evidence came out it was clear to see that it was in fact Johnny Depp. who had been suffering at her hand. With the sheer amount of awful things that she's done, we have a list of all the reasons she's been cancelled. These are the Top 10 Reasons Amber Heard Was Cancelled.

With the initial court date being pushed back, Johnny Depp and Amber Heard have been given some more time in order to gather more evidence for their individual cases. For quite some time, the two were firing evidence at each other in order to win in court. 

Ever since the recent release of the footage of the LAPD officers from the penthouse night of Amber Heard and Johnny Depp, things have not been looking all too bright for Amber Heard. Her team has been working tirelessly in order to back up her side, however Johnny Depp seems to have made the attempt to strike back.
